Keith Cameron scammed his friend and neighbour Jonathan Speirs out of £476,864 in a complicated scam . 
  He promised the world-famous lighting architect a £2million return on his investment in two years . 
  Cameron was jailed for five years at Edinburgh Sheriff Court . 
  Jonathan died of stomach cancer in 2012 and his family is now facing selling their home . 
  Cameron spent the money on a New York flat for his daughter . 
 